Title: Fix show more mode in page menu dropdowns
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1613753968
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b8

You had to use the "Show more items" button once on dropdowns with show more
items, even if "Default to show more" or "Enforce show more" was configured.
